imdb.plot outline: Hollywood. Land of dreams, of opportunity and of...okay, we all know that's BS. This comedy follows a trio of actors who are getting regular paying work, but who feel trapped by the roles they keep getting cast in. Actors stuck in an endless parade of sci-fi shlock and horror films. And I guess maybe we should mention that they're actually monsters. Not actors in makeup, not computer-generated trickery, but real monsters. Like, for real real...this is Typecast.
